---
---
<section id="about" class="about">
  <div class="container about-inner">
    <div class="about-head">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">About</p>
      <h2 class="about-heading">A historic Walnut Hills storefront.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="about-prose">
      <p>Dale Tucker opened 705 East McMillan as an art studio in 2024. It's now home to a small group of independent businesses — a shared place to work, meet, and occasionally host.</p>
      <p>The pressed tin ceilings, wood floors, and bay windows haven't changed much. The kind of work happening here has.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: clamp(80px, 12vh, 144px) clamp(24px, 6vw, 80px);
    background: var(--bg);
  }

  .about-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 56px;
    max-width: 1040px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  @media (min-width: 840px) {
    .about-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.3fr;
      gap: clamp(56px, 8vw, 112px);
      align-items: start;
    }
  }

  .about-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 4.4vw, 52px);
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    color: var(--text);
    margin: 16px 0 0;
    max-width: 14ch;
  }

  .about-prose p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: clamp(16px, 1.6vw, 18px);
    line-height: 1.72;
    color: var(--text-soft);
    margin: 0 0 20px;
    max-width: 56ch;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }

  .about-prose p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
</style>
